UID:TS1-B72B2875-CA3A-4EE3-8D2E-3930900E3F5A
DTSTART:20231010T130000
DTEND:20231010T150000
SUMMARY:CUMIRP: Intro lecture (Crosby)
DESCRIPTION:<2023-10-10 Tue 13:00-15:00>\n• 2 key parts to adhesion: wettin
